 258	
 259	4. **Add tests**:
 260	 ```typescript
 261	 describe('create', () => {
 262	 it('should create item', async () => {
 263	 // Test implementation
 264	 });
 265	 });
 266	 ```
 267	
 268	### 4. Background Jobs
 269	
 270	1. **Define job processor**:
 271	 ```typescript
 272	 @Process('job-name')
 273	 async handleJob(job: Job<JobData>) {
 274	 // Job implementation
 275	 }
 276	 ```
 277	
 278	2. **Queue job**:
 279	 ```typescript
 280	 await this.queue.add('job-name', jobData);
 281	 ```
 282	
 283	3. **Test job processing**:
 284	 ```typescript
 285	 // Test job execution
 286	 ```
